# =============================================================================
# EmailJS — contact form → your inbox
# https://www.emailjs.com/  →  Dashboard: https://dashboard.emailjs.com/
# =============================================================================
#
# SETUP (do this once):
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` in the project root (next to package.json).
# 2. Fill in the three values below from your EmailJS account.
# 3. Restart Vite: stop `npm run dev` and run it again (env is read at startup).
#
# WHERE TO FIND EACH VALUE:
# • VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID  → Email Services → your service → Service ID
# • VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID → Email Templates → your template → Template ID
# • VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY  → Account → General → Public Key
#
# EMAIL TEMPLATE (must match what the app sends):
# In the template body, use these variables so visitors’ messages reach you:
#   {{from_name}}   {{from_email}}   {{message}}
# Set the template “To Email” to the address where you want to receive mail.
#
# =============================================================================

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=service
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=templat
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=qdmsNKQA
